# Assignment 1 checklist:

Boot xv6:
Three main steps: download riscv toolchain, download qemu, download xv6. 
Just followed the instructions, and everything will work out fine.

sleep: sleep() takes no argument, so I guess it sleeps for a fixed unit of time. Check sys_sleep() and find it takes n from trap frame a1.

pingpong: 0 for READ, 1 for WRITE. Waste some time figuring this out.

primes: run a process for each layer, every pair of parent/child processes communicate by pipe

find: just find

xargs: